FAMILY 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A0477A6592DB0B29" authority="GRAY, 1849" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1849" box="[334,699,319,344]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Onychoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">
ONYCHOTEUTHIDAE 
<bibRefCitation id="B6224B66FFDBFFF7A3317A6592DB0B29" author="Gray JE" box="[568,699,319,344]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" refId="ref14816" refString="Gray JE. 1849. Catalogue of the Mollusca in the collection of the British Museum. Part I. Cephalopoda Artepedia. London: Trustees of the British Museum." type="book" year="1849">GRAY, 1849</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D20C3697FFDBFFF7A02F7A3C92E70B0E" blockId="18.[294,647,358,383]" box="[294,647,358,383]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230">(26 SPECIES IN SEVEN GENERA)</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="9AA9651CFFDBFFF7A1AA7AD591940F6E" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="D20C3697FFDBFFF7A1AA7AD5929A08A6" blockId="18.[163,779,398,727]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230">
<emphasis id="E0C7EA85FFDBFFF7A1AA7AD591400BD5" box="[163,288,399,420]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Small to massive adult-sized muscular 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA7AF7917F0BB2" authorityName="D' ORBIGNY" authorityYear="1845" box="[163,287,429,451]" class="Cephalopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="order">Oegopsida</taxonomicName>
with buccal connectives attached to the ventral borders of ventral arms; with two series of arm suckers; tentacle club with two series of hooks, hooks larger in the ventromedial series; usually without dactylus but with terminal pad; carpal locking apparatus formed by a well-defined circular region; funnel–mantle apparatus straight, reaching the anterior margin of the mantle; head with three or more occipital folds; gladius with a primary conus and usually with a prominent rostrum; without hectocotylization.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D20C3697FFDBFFF7A1AA785A91940F6E" blockId="18.[163,778,768,1311]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230">
<emphasis id="E0C7EA85FFDBFFF7A1AA785A916F0964" box="[163,271,768,789]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230">Remarks:</emphasis>
According to MolluscaBase eds (2021b), the superfamily 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A032784492FE0945" authority="Gray, 1849" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1849" box="[315,670,798,820]" class="Cephalopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="superFamily" superFamily="Onychoteuthoidea">
Onychoteuthoidea 
<bibRefCitation id="B6224B66FFDBFFF7A317784592FE0945" author="Gray JE" box="[542,670,799,820]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" refId="ref14816" refString="Gray JE. 1849. Catalogue of the Mollusca in the collection of the British Museum. Part I. Cephalopoda Artepedia. London: Trustees of the British Museum." type="book" year="1849">Gray, 1849</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
includes 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA786791120922" authorityName="Pfeffer" authorityYear="1912" box="[163,370,829,851]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Ancistrocheiridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Ancistrocheiridae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A0747867924E0922" authorityName="BERRY" authorityYear="1920" box="[381,558,829,851]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Architeuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Architeuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A333786793660922" authorityName="Pfeffer" authorityYear="1908" box="[570,774,829,851]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Brachioteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Brachioteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA780691100900" authorityName="Naef" authorityYear="1923" box="[163,368,860,882]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Cycloteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Cycloteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A08D780692050900" authorityName="Pfeffer" authorityYear="1900" box="[388,613,860,882]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Enoploteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Enoploteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A373780693630900" authorityName="Hoyle" authorityYear="1886" box="[634,771,860,882]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Gonatidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Gonatidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA7820910809E1" authorityName="Verrill" authorityYear="1881" box="[163,360,890,912]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Histioteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Histioteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A0717820922509E1" authorityName="Pfeffer" authorityYear="1912" box="[376,581,890,912]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Lepidoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Lepidoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A35D7820936509E1" authorityName="PFFEFER" authorityYear="1908" box="[596,773,890,912]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Lycoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Lycoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA78C3912A09DE" authorityName="Naef" authorityYear="1921" box="[163,330,921,943]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Neoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Neoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A05078C3924509DE" authorityName="Berry" authorityYear="1912" box="[345,549,921,943]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Octopoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Octopoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A33A78C3936509DE" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1849" box="[563,773,921,943]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Onychoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Onychoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA78E291C109BC" authorityName="Voss" authorityYear="1956" box="[163,417,952,974]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Pholidoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Pholidoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A0C978E292A309BC" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1920" box="[448,707,952,974]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Psychroteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Psychroteuthidae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA788C9139099D" authorityName="Pfeffer" authorityYear="1912" box="[163,345,982,1004]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Pyroteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Pyroteuthidae</taxonomicName>
. This taxonomic composition does not agree with the phylogeny provided here, but this name can be resurrected with a new diagnosis for 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A05C7F6892400E39" authorityName="Verrill" authorityYear="1881" box="[341,544,1074,1096]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Histioteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Histioteuthidae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A33B7F68936A0E39" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1849" box="[562,778,1074,1096]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Onychoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Onychoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1ED7F0891B70E16" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1920" box="[228,471,1105,1127]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Psychroteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Psychroteuthidae</taxonomicName>
if the morphological support provided by 
<bibRefCitation id="B6224B66FFDBFFF7A0A67F2A936A0EF7" author="Young RE &amp; Vecchione M" box="[431,778,1136,1158]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" refId="ref18209" refString="Young RE, Vecchione M. 2016 a. Histioteuthid families. Version 29 August 2016 (under construction). Available at: http: // tolweb. org / Histioteuthid _ families / 19415 / 2016.08.29" type="url" year="2016">Young &amp; Vecchione (2016a)</bibRefCitation>
for a relationship between 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A3387FD593690ED5" authorityName="Verrill" authorityYear="1881" box="[561,777,1166,1188]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Histioteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Histioteuthidae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1D77FF791A00EB2" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1920" box="[222,448,1197,1219]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Psychroteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Psychroteuthidae</taxonomicName>
and the weak molecular support provided here for a relationship between 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A1AA7FB091380F71" authorityName="Verrill" authorityYear="1881" box="[163,344,1258,1280]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Histioteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Histioteuthidae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="15B34D14FFDBFFF7A09B7FB092370F71" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1849" box="[402,599,1258,1280]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Onychoteuthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Oegopsida" pageId="18" pageNumber="1230" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Onychoteuthidae</taxonomicName>
is supported in future phylogenetic analyses.
</paragraph>
